          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1620229730638-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper (squeeze as much liquid out as you can!)</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
